'''Dragon Quest III: Soshite Densetsu e...''' (そして伝説へ..., "And Into the Legend...") is the Super Famicom remake of the original NES Dragon Warrior III. It features completely redrawn graphics, orchestrated music, and numerous gameplay enhancements.

==Overview==

The SNES remake expands significantly on the original:
* New personality system affecting stat growth
* Additional mini-games
* Monster medals collection
* Enhanced graphics and sound
* Pachisi/Sugoroku mini-game tracks

